	<a href="https://calmatters.org/author/nigelduara/" class="author">By Nigel Duara <img alt='Nigel Duara' src='https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/01/download-e1578450993429-96x96.jpeg' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/nigelduara" class="author-twitter"><svg role="img" class="icon icon--twitter" aria-label="twitter"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#twitter"></use></svg></a>	<span class="published">published: <time datetime="2020-04-17T17:12:14-07:00">April 17, 2020</time></span>
