				<h2 class="largeheadline ">A-list business and union leaders combine to help steer California&#8217;s economic recovery</h2>
				<div class="featured-image">
	<div class="image">
		<img width="794" height="529" src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?fit=794%2C529" class="attachment-large-wide-rec size-large-wide-rec wp-post-image" alt="A hopeful message is seen on the marquee of the The Chabot theatre on Castro Valley Boulevard day nine of the coronavirus stay-at-home order in Castro Valley, Calif., on March 26, 2020. Photo by Jane Tyska, Bay Area News Group" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=2000 2000w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=1536 1536w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=460 460w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=321 321w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=858 858w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/SJM_taskforce_01.jpg?w=794 794w" sizes="(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px" />	</div>
	<div class="imagebyline">
					<svg role="img" class="icon icon--camera" aria-label="camera"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#camera"></use></svg>			<span>A hopeful message is seen on the marquee of the The Chabot theatre on Castro Valley Boulevard day nine of the coronavirus stay-at-home order in Castro Valley, Calif., on March 26, 2020. Photo by Jane Tyska, Bay Area News Group</span>
			</div>
</div>
			</div>

			
